{"id":232813532,"title":"二輪騎隧道超危險？@@","content":"我在半年前騎著R3要從彰化去到南投\n看GOOGLEMAP有2條路給我選\n1條是139山道\n1條是八卦山隧道\n當時時間晚上8點多\n139是伸手不見5指的狀態\n下意識的選擇騎有燈的八卦山隧道\n路超亮超直\n速限80我表速訂在80騎  右手很乖\n旁邊一堆汽車超我車  肉眼測速破100\n\n\n隔了1個月有一個Z1000的車友問我說彰化要怎麼騎到南投\n我跟他說騎八卦山隧道很快就到\n他跟我說那邊不能騎我一定會收到罰單\n我還不相信\n還特地拿手機出來查給他看.....還真的不能騎.....打我自己的臉\n\n\nPS..之後跟Z1000同行的忍400走139還被拍國家級追焦\n    那天新聞139還有車禍\n從此以後有人跟我說隧道很危險我都聽不下去\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7fdb485b-0240-45aa-a5e5-2a3a411b8761/1280.jpeg\n附一張車展的圖\n\n真人真事沒有改編","excerpt":"我在半年前騎著R3要從彰化去到南投，看GOOGLEMAP有2條路給我選，1條是139山道，1條是八卦山隧道，當時時間晚上8點多，139是伸手不見5指的狀態，下意識的選擇騎有燈的八卦山隧道，路超亮超直，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2cffc289-d332-4d4e-95a7-cae58a1778aa","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-02T16:13:38.528Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T16:13:38.528Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":43,"tags":[],"topics":["隧道","路權"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"重機","forumAlias":"heavy_motorcycle","school":"技術不值錢","department":"lion860919zz","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":43}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7fdb485b-0240-45aa-a5e5-2a3a411b8761/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a8ee7006-9486-4231-84cc-f3bea2d18073","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7fdb485b-0240-45aa-a5e5-2a3a411b8761/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7fdb485b-0240-45aa-a5e5-2a3a411b8761/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7fdb485b-0240-45aa-a5e5-2a3a411b8761/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-02T16:13:38.528Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T16:13:38.528Z","width":640,"height":480},{"id":"a8ee7006-9486-4231-84cc-f3bea2